text: Hip, comfortable, perfectly located, you can't go wrong with Casa Soco!  I rented this house with a few friends for a wedding weekend. Having never been to Austin, we were especially appreciative of host Ashley's extra efforts to welcome us. She left cupcakes and Lone Star in the fridge as well as several very helpful guides to the city. I would recommend this place over and over again!
title: Modern, Urban Oasis for 8 SoCo/SoFi
